            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> spaghetti</strong> and return to the pot, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
