      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are beginning to soften, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and<strong> crushed fennel seeds</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add the<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for a further 30 secs</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
