    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then add to the pan along with the <strong>'Nduja </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined and the spinach has wilted</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for a further 3-4 min or until a sauce has formed</p>",
      "order": 5,
